    "<span class=\"word\">The men of <span class=\"place\">Nineveh</span> shall rise in judgment with this generation, and shall condemn it: because they repented at the preaching of <span class=\"person\">Jonas</span>; and, behold, a greater than <span class=\"person\">Jonas</span> is here.</span> ",
    "<span class=\"word\">The queen of the south shall rise up in the judgment with this generation, and shall condemn it: for she came from the uttermost parts of the earth to hear the wisdom of <span class=\"person\">Solomon</span>; and, behold, a greater than <span class=\"person\">Solomon</span> is here.</span> ",
