    "#<span class=\"word\">For this people's heart is waxed gross,</span>#<span class=\"word\">and their ears are dull of hearing, and their eyes they have closed;</span>#<span class=\"word\">lest at any time they should see with their eyes and hear with their ears,</span>#<span class=\"word\">and should understand with their heart,</span>#<span class=\"word\">and should be converted, and I should heal them.</span> ",
    "#<span class=\"word\">But blessed are your eyes, for they see: and your ears, for they hear.</span> ",
