    "Another parable put he forth unto them, saying, <span class=\"word\">The kingdom of heaven is likened unto a man which sowed good seed in his field:</span> ",
    "<span class=\"word\">But while men slept, his enemy came and sowed tares among the wheat, and went his way.</span> ",
