    "<span class=\"word\">The enemy that sowed them is the devil; the harvest is the end of the world; and the reapers are the angels.</span> ",
    "<span class=\"word\">As therefore the tares are gathered and burned in the fire; so shall it be in the end of this world.</span> ",
