    "<span class=\"word\">And he came to the second, and said likewise. And he answered and said, I go, sir: and went not.</span> ",
    "<span class=\"word\">Whether of them twain did the will of his father?</span> They say unto him, The first. <span class=\"person\">Jesus</span> saith unto them, <span class=\"word\">Verily I say unto you, That the publicans and the harlots go into the kingdom of God before you.</span> ",
