    "<span class=\"word\">Thou oughtest therefore to have put my money to the exchangers, and then at my coming I should have received mine own with usury.</span> ",
    "<span class=\"word\">Take therefore the talent from him, and give it unto him which hath ten talents.</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">For unto every one that hath shall be given, and he shall have abundance: but from him that hath not shall be taken away even that which he hath.</span> ",
    "<span class=\"word\">And cast ye the unprofitable servant into outer darkness: there shall be weeping and gnashing of teeth.</span> ",
